Package: drawsneeded
Type: Package
Title: Estimates the number of samples at least needed to ascertain a minimum error
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person(
      "Crist-Jan", "Doedens",
      email = "cjd@chance-matters.nl",
      role = c("aut", "cre")
    )
  )
Description: In an audit of monetary expenses we might use sampling to establish
   an estimate of the error rate in a mass of monetary transactions.
   For planning the number of necessary samples we can use the function exported by
   this tiny package.
